Build a modern React TypeScript (TSX) web app called "Keyboard Warrior Arena".

The app should have a dark cyberpunk UI with neon accents, smooth animations, and a highly interactive design.

Core features:

- Real-time typing test with a displayed paragraph
- Track typing speed (WPM), accuracy, and error count
- Implement a "rage meter" that increases when the user presses backspace frequently or makes rapid mistakes
- Show live funny commentary based on performance (e.g., slow typing, high errors, rage level)
- Include a simulated opponent that types with dynamic speed and mistakes to mimic real gameplay
- Display a results screen with WPM, accuracy, rage level, and winner
- Add a shareable result card UI

Use Tailwind CSS for styling and Framer Motion for animations.

Ensure the UI is highly polished, responsive, and visually engaging.